snippet: A strong quake struck off northern Chile on Sunday evening, triggering a brief evacuation of part of the coastal area but not causing any injuries or significant damage....

headline.print_headline: Strong Quake Jolts Chile's North, No Major Damage
headline.main: Strong Quake Jolts Chile's North, No Major Damage

lead_paragraph: A strong quake struck off northern Chile on Sunday evening, triggering a brief evacuation of part of the coastal area but not causing any injuries or significant damage.
